names.name: Shaddai El Chai
names.description: The Divine Name associated with Yesod, representing the foundation of God's presence in the world.

names.name: Gabriel
names.description: The Archangel known as the Messenger of God, associated with revelation and the interpretation of dreams.

names.name: Cherubim
names.description: The order of angels associated with Yesod, symbolizing the guardians of God's glory.

names.name: Moon
names.description: The planetary influence associated with Yesod, representing the reflection of the divine light and the rhythms of life.

names.name: Levanah
names.description: Symbolizes the purity and the foundational truth that underlies creation.

names.name: Tsadik
names.description: Reflects the attribute of righteousness as the moral foundation of actions.
